init_text: When you die, you appear in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you. You find out that they are your previous reincarnations, and soon you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You are a God-like figure who has the power to grant miracles to those you deem worthy.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: A person can only receive one miracle in their lifetime, so you must choose carefully who will have the ultimate reward.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: What happens if you give a miracle to someone who does not deserve it?

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Or what happens if you give the wrong miracle to the right person?

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Through your decisions, you will be shaping their lives and the lives of everyone they come in contact with.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They will be grateful for the miracle and will give it back to you by continuing to spread the gift in their own lives.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Over time, you will see the effect of these miracles.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You would want to live a life where you could really make a difference, wouldn't you?

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You have a chance to make a difference in the life of someone else.
